{"name":"Beast and Briar","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>A violent encounter with a wild beast or the sting of poisonous nettles nearly laid you low. When you survived, you discovered your experience had changed you. Not only were you aware of the inconstant boundary between life and death, you also found you had a connection to the natural world.</p><div data-source=\"BH:SP\" class=\"rd__b refreshing-brew rd__b--2\"><h3 class=\"rd__h rd__h--2\" data-title-index=\"3532\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Expanded Spell List</span><span class=\"ve-flex-vh-center\"> <span class=\"rd__title-link \"><span class=\"help-subtle\" title=\"Spiritualist\">BH:SP</span> p7</span><span class=\"rd__h-toggle ml-2 clickable\" data-rd-h-toggle-button=\"true\">[–]</span></span></h3> <p>The nature of your near death experience expands the magic available to you. The following spells are added to the spiritualist spell list for you.</p><table class=\"w-100 rd__table  stripe-odd-table\"><caption>Beast and Briar Expanded Spells</caption><thead><tr><th class=\"col-3 text-center\" data-rd-isroller=\"false\">Spell Levels</th><th class=\"col-9\" data-rd-isroller=\"false\">Spells</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class=\"col-3 text-center\">1st</td><td class=\"col-9\">@spell[animal friendship], @spell[entangle]</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-3 text-center\">2nd</td><td class=\"col-9\">@spell[animal messenger], @spell[spike growth]</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-3 text-center\">3rd</td><td class=\"col-9\">@spell[conjure animals], @spell[plant growth]</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-3 text-center\">4th</td><td class=\"col-9\">@spell[grasping vine], @spell[polymorph]</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-3 text-center\">5th</td><td class=\"col-9\">@spell[commune with nature], @spell[tree stride]</td></tr></tbody></table></div><div data-source=\"BH:SP\" class=\"rd__b refreshing-brew rd__b--2\"><h3 class=\"rd__h rd__h--2\" data-title-index=\"3533\"> <span class=\"