{"name":"Killing Field","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>At 14th level, you can use an action to suffuse the area around you with violent energy. When you do, on each of your turns for the next minute you can use a bonus action to cause harm to a creature you can see within 60 feet. If the creature's current hit points equal its hit point maximum, it takes [[/r 1d6]] necrotic damage. If the creature's current hit points equal more than half its hit point maximum, it takes [[/r 2d6]] necrotic damage. If the creature's current hit points are equal to or less than its hit point maximum, it takes [[/r 3d6]] necrotic damage. After you use this feature, you must finish a long rest before you can use it again.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"BH:SP","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d6","necrotic"],["2d6","necrotic"],["3d6","necrotic"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Spiritualist 14 (Bloody Blade)","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"BH:SP","hash":"killing%20field_spiritualist_bh%3asp_bloody%20blade_bh%3asp_14_bh%3asp","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"f3d226d94c34ca68891f9a8d0896477a4f71dc09"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004948792,"modifiedTime":1682004948792,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"tS3pxbxZK6hVvjZt"}
{"name":"Plague and Poison","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>Just when a disease or toxin brought you to the brink of death, your fever broke and you survived. The foreign element that nearly killed you left a stain on your soul, giving you an unnatural affinity for plagues and poisons. Some spiritualists of this threshold appear perpetually ill or afflicted by the toxin that nearly killed them.</p><div data-source=\"BH:SP\" class=\"rd__b refreshing-brew rd__b--2\"><h3 class=\"rd__h rd__h--2\" data-title-index=\"3539\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Expanded Spell List</span><span class=\"ve-flex-vh-center\"> <span class=\"rd__title-link \"><span class=\"help-subtle\" title=\"Spiritualist\">BH:SP</span> p8</span><span class=\"rd__h-toggle ml-2 clickable\" data-rd-h-toggle-button=\"true\">[–]</span></span></h3> <p>The nature of your near death experience expands the magic available to you. The following spells are added to the spiritualist spell list for you.</p><table class=\"w-100 rd__table  stripe-odd-table\"><caption>Plague and Poison Expanded Spells</caption><thead><tr><th class=\"col-3 text-center\" data-rd-isroller=\"false\">Spell Levels</th><th class=\"col-9\" data-rd-isroller=\"false\">Spells</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class=\"col-3 text-center\">1st</td><td class=\"col-9\">@spell[detect poison and disease], @spell[purify food and drink]</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-3 text-center\">2nd</td><td class=\"col-9\">@spell[melf's acid arrow], @spell[protection from poison]</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-3 text-center\">3rd</td><td class=\"col-9\">@spell[gaseous form], @spell[vampiric touch]</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-3 text-center\">4th</td><td class=\"col-9\">@spell[blight], @spell[sickening radiance|XGE]</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-3 text-center\">5th</td><td class=\"col-9\">@spell[contagion], @spell[enervation|XGE]</td></tr></tbody></table></div><div data-source=\"BH:SP\" class=\"rd__b refreshing-brew rd__b--2\"><h3 class=\"rd__h rd__h--2\" data-title-index=\"3540\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Inured to Toxins</span><span class=\"ve-flex-vh-center\"> <span class=\"rd__title-link \"><span class=\"help-subtle\" title=\"Spiritualist\">BH:SP</span> p8</span><span class=\"rd__h-toggle ml-2 clickable\" data-rd-h-toggle-button=\"true\">[–]</span></span></h3> <p>Starting when you take this threshold at 1st level, you have resistance to poison damage. In addition, you have advantage on saving throws against disease and being @condition[poisoned].</p></div></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"BH:SP","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Spiritualist 1 (Plague and Poison)","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"BH:SP","hash":"plague%20and%20poison_spiritualist_bh%3asp_plague%20and%20poison_bh%3asp_1_bh%3asp","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"bf210d4439a3405b4843c011b52464ff0cab933a"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004948828,"modifiedTime":1682004948828,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"SPV94W2HfZ7jMeQC"}
{"name":"Expanded Spell List","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>The nature of your near death experience expands the magic available to you. The following spells are added to the spiritualist spell list for you.</p><table class=\"w-100 rd__table  stripe-odd-table\"><caption>Plague and Poison Expanded Spells</caption><thead><tr><th class=\"col-3 text-center\" data-rd-isroller=\"false\">Spell Levels</th><th class=\"col-9\" data-rd-isroller=\"false\">Spells</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class=\"col-3 text-center\">1st</td><td class=\"col-9\">@spell[detect poison and disease], @spell[purify food and drink]</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-3 text-center\">2nd</td><td class=\"col-9\">@spell[melf's acid arrow], @spell[protection from poison]</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-3 text-center\">3rd</td><td class=\"col-9\">@spell[gaseous form], @spell[vampiric touch]</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-3 text-center\">4th</td><td class=\"col-9\">@spell[blight], @spell[sickening radiance|XGE]</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-3 text-center\">5th</td><td class=\"col-9\">@spell[contagion], @spell[enervation|XGE]</td></tr></tbody></table></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"BH:SP","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Spiritualist 1 (Plague and Poison)","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/control/encase-creature-monster-hold.webp","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"BH:SP","hash":"expanded%20spell%20list_spiritualist_bh%3as