{"name":"Stygian Inhalation","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>At 10th level, you can inhale the deathly vapors let off by living creatures as they pass. When a living creature within 30 feet of you dies, you can use your reaction to gain temporary hit points equal to twice your level in this class. While you have temporary hit points granted by this feature, wisps of black smoke escape your mouth when you speak and you have resistance to nonmagical damage. Once you use this feature, you must finish a short or long rest before you can use it again.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"BH:SP","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":"When a living creature within 30 feet of you dies, you can use"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"sr","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Spiritualist 10","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"adnd5e":{"itemInfo":{"type":"reaction"}},"plutonium":{"page":"classFeature","source":"BH:SP","hash":"stygian%20inhalation_spiritualist_bh%3asp_10_bh%3asp","propDroppable":"classFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"6b4425581eeb3d29d1d47bec4b4063a4a5cf6c9f"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004949216,"modifiedTime":1682004949216,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"4PaqogDxXZsnluG0"}
{"name":"Occult Insight (6th level)","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>At 11th level, your spiritual power evolves, giving you the ability to cast higher level spells. Each time you finish a long rest, you can choose one <a href=\"https://5etools-mirror-1.github.io/spells.html#blankhash,flstlevel:6=1,flstclass:spiritualist%20(bh%3asp)=1\">6th level spiritualist spell</a>. You can cast that spell without expending a spell slot and must finish a long rest before you can do so again.</p><p>At higher levels, you gain the ability to cast additional spiritualist spells in the same way: at 13th level you can choose one <a href=\"https://5etools-mirror-1.github.io/spells.html#blankhash,flstlevel:7=1,flstclass:spiritualist%20(bh%3asp)=1\">7th level spell</a>, at 15th level you can choose one <a href=\"https://5etools-mirror-1.github.io/spells.html#blankhash,flstlevel:8=1,flstclass:spiritualist%20(bh%3asp)=1\">8th level spell</a>, and at 17th level you can choose one <a href=\"https://5etools-mirror-1.github.io/spells.html#blankhash,flstlevel:9=1,flstclass:spiritualist%20(bh%3asp)=1\">9th level spell</a>. You regain the ability to cast a spell of each of these levels with this feature when you finish a long rest.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"BH:SP","activation":{"type":"special","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Spiritualist 11","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"cl